main

Class BookLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.BookLibrary

  • public class BookLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the book library information. It has three properties: bookList, existingIds, and idCounter. All three properties have getters and methods to alter them. The idCounter getter also increments it.
